 first grain to grain transfer, ensuring you never run out.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The above is how I keep supermarkets stocked with a constant supply of fresh product from our &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mushroomvideos.com/Mountain-Mushroom-Farm&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer noopener&quot;&gt;mushroom farm&lt;/a&gt;, all from a single master culture slant.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>15989458</next>\n<prev>15989365</prev>\n<first>15989365</first>\n<last>16088616</last>\n<when>1332608391</when>\n<utime>03/24/12 07:59 PM</utime>\n</post>"}